title: Perception, Action, & Development Lab
text:
The UCR Perception, Action, & Development Lab studies:

Natural visual and motor experiences of infants, children, and adults in activities of daily living
Visual exploration of complex scenes and everyday environments
Perceptual recalibration to changing motor abilities
